  "commit_message": "fix(redis): prevent _pending_messages memory leak in ResultConsumer (#10342)\n\n* fix(redis): prevent _pending_messages memory leak in ResultConsumer\n\nWhen on_wait_for_pending polls the backend synchronously and the task\nis already in a READY state, _iter_meta resolves the result and removes\nit from _pending_results. Calling the full on_state_change afterwards\nwould buffer the meta in _pending_messages because the result is no\nlonger tracked, causing entries to be retained until the buffer evicts\n",
